{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"arthrodial-slate-fallowdeer","description":"## Why\nDeferred post-deployment measurement for the 2026-07-12 calibration follow-up epic\n(9d50-ead1-de68-4362 / unrational-expansive-catfish). That epic ships three\nbehavior changes — code-review serious-tier blocking (b9c0), the loosened\nadvisory-remediation guidance (e1f2), and the G7 leaf-parent-containment criterion\n(d4cf) — whose *effect* can only be observed as field data AFTER deployment over an\nobservation window. The epic itself closes on the measurement FRAMEWORK being in\nplace (its AC2); this ticket records the ACTUAL telemetry once it exists, so the\nunobservable-in-session target does not leave the epic in limbo.\n\n## What\nRun the measurement queries captured in the epic's measurement-framework comment\nafter an observation window (target: ~1–2 weeks of post-deploy change traffic) and\nrecord the results as a comment on the epic (and here):\n\n- **Code-review blocking outcome:** count of `LLM-Review: BLOCK — finding` votes and\n  the false-block count over the post-flip corpus, from the `REVIEW_RESULT`\n  (code_review_result_v1) sidecars in `.tickets-tracker`, compared to the pre-change\n  baseline (0 finding-blocks / 162 changes).\n- **Plan-review advisory uptake:** advisory `norm_id` survival across review rounds\n  (a surviving-then-disappearing advisory = an advisory the agent chose to address),\n  and rounds-to-pass, before vs after the e1f2 guidance loosening.\n- **G7 fire-rate:** the parent-containment criterion's fire-rate + adjudication from\n  its `REVIEW_RESULT` sidecars (feeds d4cf's promotion decision).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] [operator-attested] The post-deployment observation window has elapsed and the\n      three measurement queries above have been run against the post-change corpus;\n      evidence is a comment recording the actual counts/rates with the query commands\n      and the window dates.\n- [ ] The results are posted as a comment on epic 9d50-ead1-de68-4362, closing the\n      loop on its measurement framework.","id":"72b6-b0d2-2f93-456d","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Deferred: record post-deployment field data for the 2026-07-12 calibration epic"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783883704013095001,"uuid":"103abef8-f204-4a0a-bee2-2b411cc321b8"}